title: HelloGitHub Monthly
description: Discover development tools, open source books, tutorials, and enterprise-level projects that make programming fun and foster a love for open source.
p_text: “HelloGitHub Monthly” shares interesting and beginner-friendly open source projects on GitHub. Published on the 28th of each month, it includes development tools, open source books, tutorials, and enterprise-level projects to help you discover the joy of programming and fall in love with open source!
